0.3 - 2004-09-

        * Feature: new buttons to delete Jpeg files
        * Feature: --nodelete option to prevent the display of delete buttons
        * Feature: Bindings so that the Escape key closes the windows
        * Feature: Larger pictures rotated according to the Orientation field
        * Feature: Photographs sorted by date
        * Bugfix: typos in POD.

0.2 - 2004-09-22

	* Feature: --dummy option to allow testing without actually modifying any
          Jpeg file
        * Bugfix: modifying an existing comment would cause a crash.
        * Feature: setting a comment to an empty string actually deletes it

0.1 - 2004-09-21

	* Initial release
